content.rendered:
Collector | Tulsa, Oklahoma
  • Full-time, Monday-Friday 8am-5pm
  • Medical collection experience a plus
  • Must have billing knowledge and be able to read an EOB
  • Preference given to those with 2+ years  recent experience in medical collecting
  • $12+/hour depending on experience
